25 carry the firearm in the line of duty.
26 (3) An individual who takes a firearm from the lawful
27 possession of a peace officer or a corrections officer is guilty of
28 a felony punishable by imprisonment for not more than 20 years or a
29 fine of not more than $5,000.00, or both, if all of the following
